#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.16"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.16:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Mahāvagga"
msgstr "2. The Great Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Dūteyyasutta"
msgstr "16. Going on a Mission"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.196"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.16:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu dūteyyaṃ gantumarahati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a mendicant with eight qualities is worthy of going on a "
"mission."

msgctxt "an8.16:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.16:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sotā ca hoti, sāvetā ca, uggahetā ca, dhāretā ca, "
"viññātā ca, viññāpetā ca, kusalo ca sahitāsahitassa, no ca kalahakārako—"
msgstr ""
"It’s a mendicant who learns and educates others. They memorize and help "
"others remember. They understand and help others understand. They’re skilled "
"at knowing what’s on topic and what isn’t. And they don’t cause quarrels."

msgctxt "an8.16:1.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu dūteyyaṃ "
"gantumarahati."
msgstr "A mendicant with these eight qualities is worthy of going on a mission."

msgctxt "an8.16:1.5"
msgid ""
"Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato sāriputto dūteyyaṃ gantumarahati."
msgstr "With eight qualities Sāriputta is worthy of going on a mission."

msgctxt "an8.16:1.6"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.16:1.7"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, sāriputto sotā ca hoti, sāvetā ca, uggahetā ca, dhāretā ca, "
"viññātā ca, viññāpetā ca, kusalo ca sahitāsahitassa, no ca kalahakārako."
msgstr ""
"He learns and educates others. He memorizes and helps others remember. He "
"understands and helps others understand. He’s skilled at knowing what’s on "
"topic and what isn’t. And he doesn’t cause quarrels."

msgctxt "an8.16:1.8"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahi dhammehi samannāgato sāriputto dūteyyaṃ "
"gantumarahatīti."
msgstr "With these eight qualities Sāriputta is worthy of going on a mission."

# Reading navedhati
#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: na byathati → navedhati (bj) | na byādhati (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an8.16:2.1"
msgid "Yo ve na byathati patvā,"
msgstr "They don’t tremble when arriving"

#. <br>
#. VAR: uggavādiniṃ → uggavādinaṃ (si) | uggahavādinaṃ (s1-3, pts1) | uggatavādiniṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an8.16:2.2"
msgid "parisaṃ uggavādiniṃ;"
msgstr "at an assembly of fierce debaters."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.16:2.3"
msgid "Na ca hāpeti vacanaṃ,"
msgstr "They don’t omit any words,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.16:2.4"
msgid "na ca chādeti sāsanaṃ."
msgstr "or conceal the instructions."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.16:3.1"
msgid "Asandiddhañca bhaṇati,"
msgstr "Their words aren’t poisoned,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.16:3.2"
msgid "Pucchito na ca kuppati;"
msgstr "and they don’t tremble when questioned."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.16:3.3"
msgid "Sa ve tādisako bhikkhu,"
msgstr "Such a mendicant"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.16:3.4"
msgid "Dūteyyaṃ gantumarahatī”ti."
msgstr "is worthy of going on a mission.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.16:3.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
